=== ERROR PREVENTION ===

NEVER do these:
❌ Put content outside tagged sections
❌ Use wrong tag format: <TEXT> or [TEXT] or @TEXT@
❌ Use JSON format for tool calls
❌ Forget closing tags
❌ Mix tagged and untagged content

